{"title_page": "Jiangbeizui CBD", "text_new": "{{Coord missing|Chongqing}}\n\n[[File:CQ Science Museum.JPG|thumb|The [[Chongqing Science & Technology Museum]] in Jiangbeizui CBD.]]\n\n'''Jiangbeizui CBD''' ([[Central business district|Central Business District]]) is a part of [[Liangjiang New Area]] in central [[Chongqing]], [[China]].\n\n<!-- The CBD covers an area of 50,000 km<sup>2</sup>. -->\nThe CBD aims to attract financial institutions, making it a [[financial center]] in the future.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://english.liangjiang.gov.cn/2014-01/07/content_17229036.htm | title=Jiangbeizui Financial Center | publisher=[http://english.liangjiang.gov.cn/ Chongqing Liangjiang New Area] | location=China | date=7 January 2014 | accessdate=23 August 2014 }}</ref> It is expected to be completed in 2018.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://en.cq.gov.cn/ChongqingToday/News/3998.htm | title=Chongqing Jiangbeizui CBD takes shape and is expected to be fully completed by 2018 | publisher=[[Chongqing Municipal Government]] | date=17 June 2013 | accessdate=23 August 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052559/http://en.cq.gov.cn/ChongqingToday/News/3998.htm | archive-date=4 March 2016 | url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nJiangbeizui CBD is located by the [[Yangtze|Yangtze River]], near the confluence with the [[Jialing River]] immediately across Chongqing city's primary downtown hub of [[Jiefangbei CBD]]. The world class [[Chongqing Science and Technology Museum]] is located here.\n\n==See also==\n* [[Jiefangbei CBD]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Chongqing-geo-stub}}\n\n[[Category:Economy of Chongqing]]\n[[Category:Geography of Chongqing]]\n[[Category:Central business districts]]\n[[Category:Financial districts in China]]\n", "text_old": "[[File:CQ Science Museum.JPG|thumb|The [[Chongqing Science & Technology Museum]] in Jiangbeizui CBD.]]\n\n'''Jiangbeizui CBD''' ([[Central Business District]]) is a part of [[Liangjiang New Area]] in central [[Chongqing]], [[China]].\n\n<!-- The CBD covers an area of 50,000 km<sup>2</sup>. -->\nThe CBD aims to attract financial institutions, making it a [[financial center]] in the future.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://english.liangjiang.gov.cn/2014-01/07/content_17229036.htm | title=Jiangbeizui Financial Center | publisher=[http://english.liangjiang.gov.cn/ Chongqing Liangjiang New Area] | location=China | date=7 January 2014 | accessdate=23 August 2014 }}</ref> It is expected to be completed in 2018.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://en.cq.gov.cn/ChongqingToday/News/3998.htm | title=Chongqing Jiangbeizui CBD takes shape and is expected to be fully completed by 2018 | publisher=[[Chongqing Municipal Government]] | date=17 June 2013 | accessdate=23 August 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052559/http://en.cq.gov.cn/ChongqingToday/News/3998.htm | archive-date=4 March 2016 | url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nJiangbeizui CBD is located by the [[Yangtze River]], near the confluence with the [[Jialing River]] immediately across Chongqing city's primary downtown hub of [[Jeifangbei CBD]]. The world class [[Chongqing Science and Technology Museum]] is located here.\n\n==See also==\n* [[Jeifangbei CBD]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{coord missing|Chongqing}}\n\n{{Chongqing-geo-stub}}\n\n[[Category:Economy of Chongqing]]\n[[Category:Geography of Chongqing]]\n[[Category:Central business districts]]\n[[Category:Financial districts in China]]\n", "name_user": "Xindeho", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jiangbeizui_CBD"}
